---
---
<section id="before-after" class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-center text-navy mb-4">
      まるっと回収 ビフォーアフター
    </h2>
    <p class="text-center text-warm-gray mb-12">
      買取品も不用品もまとめてお引き取り。お部屋をスッキリさせます。
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Before -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-4 border-2 border-dashed border-cream-dark">
          <div class="text-navy/30 mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/>
              <rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/>
              <rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/>
              <rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-warm-gray text-sm">不用品が散乱した状態</p>
        </div>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-warm-gray/10 text-warm-gray font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm">
          Before
        </span>
      </div>

      <!-- Arrow (mobile: down, desktop: hidden - implied by side-by-side) -->
      <div class="flex md:hidden justify-center -my-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-gold" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/>
          <polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <!-- After -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-4 border-2 border-gold/30">
          <div class="text-gold/50 mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-warm-gray text-sm">スッキリきれいなお部屋に</p>
        </div>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gold/10 text-gold font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm">
          After
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-warm-gray text-sm mt-8">
      大型家電や家具の搬出も、スタッフが丁寧に対応します。
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
